    "abstractNote": "\u00abThe aim of this paper therefore is to find out the characteristic features of the contemporary charismatic renewal mplied throughout the homily of Mar Narsai on pentecost. The main features we look for are: (1) Baptism in the Spirit (Effusion of the Holy Spirit), (2) Joyful praise, (3) Gift of Tongues, (4) Prophecy, 5) Healing, Renewal and conversion.\u00bb (P. 126)",
